  "description": "This dataset is a supplement to the article \" β-catenin deficiency in\n forebrain excitatory neurons induces fear memory deficits and\n physiological alterations.\" The dataset comprises a suite of scripts\n designed to analyze the data obtained in ABF format following the\n execution of a series of standard electrophysiological protocols. The\n execution of these scripts occurs over every ABF file contained within a\n folder, in an unsupervised manner, methodically analyzing a series of\n commonly calculated futures from each protocol.",
